Install KDE:
sudo dnf groupinstall "KDE Plasma Workspaces"
Install Fcitx5 https://wiki.archlinux.org/title/Fcitx5
Use im-chooser to chose Fcitx5 as defaut IME
Install fcitx5-rime
Set the following environment variables in `~/.config/environment.d/im.conf`
```
GTK_IM_MODULE=fcitx
QT_IM_MODULE=fcitx
XMODIFIERS=@im=fcitx
```
